cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper deals with image analysis and labeling, which is a core area of computer vision.
2. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper deals with outdoor scene layout labeling, which is related to graphics and visualization.
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a system that uses both local features and global attributes to improve labeling results, which is related to AI and machine learning.
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a system that integrates global attributes in the conditional random field (CRF) framework to improve labeling results, which is related to machine learning.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with image analysis and labeling, which is related to multimedia.
